commentTextItems.html: short of a length and down the leg side, Badani pulls the ball hard to the midwicket fence, that's the India win and Badani's half century!

commentPostTextItems.html: That is the end of a comprehensive win for India
Victory by 9 wickets and India have their first points of the Coca Cola Cup
We hope you enjoyed the coverage on www.cricinfo.com, we had a great time bringing it to you
Mail all your comments about the coverage to comms@cricinfo.com as always!
Thank you all for joining us at Harare, see you again for the third match on 27th for all the action!

commentTextItems.html: short of a lenth and outside the off, punched to covers
short of a length and outside the off, left alone

commentPostTextItems.html: Just one run to win now
Badani needs 2 for his half century
